---
layout: base.njk
title: Frequently Asked Questions
description: Find answers to common questions about the Central Utah Tree Festival, including how to participate, donate, and get support for families traveling to Primary Children's Hospital.
keywords: Central Utah Tree Festival FAQ, frequently asked questions, tree festival help, donate, volunteer, Sanpete County
givebutter: true
---

{% block head %}
<!-- FAQ Schema Markup for Rich Snippets -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
        {% for category in faq.categories %}
        {% for item in category.questions %}
        {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "{{ item.question }}",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "{{ item.answer }}"
            }
        }{% if not loop.last or not loop.parent.last %},{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        {% endfor %}
    ]
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

<div class="faq-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="faq-header">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="faq-intro">
            Find answers to common questions about the Central Utah Tree Festival.
            If you don't see your question here, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Categories -->
    <div class="faq-categories">
        {% for category in faq.categories %}
        <div class="faq-category">
            <h2>{{ category.name }}</h2>

            {% for item in category.questions %}
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">{{ item.question }}</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">{{ item.answer | safe }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div class="faq-cta">
        <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
        <p>We're here to help! Reach out to us and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        <div class="faq-cta-buttons">
            <a href="/contact/" class="faq-btn">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="/#donate" class="faq-btn btn-secondary">Donate Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
